<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>byḥbny mwt</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - (dạ ṣlyby msẖ ṣlybh sẖạl hw ạldẖnb lyh
 dh kạn dyn ʿlyạ rḍy lyh ybqy̱ ʿlyh)2
 1- kạn ʿqạb kẖṭyty mwt rḍy hw lyh ʿny ymwt
 jạwb wqạl byḥbny mwt wạkẖtạr ymwt ʿlsẖạny
 yạ try̱ sẖạf fyạ ạ̹yh ḥlw ʿsẖạn ạ̉tḥb ʿlyh
 ywm ạlṣlyb nẓrẗ ʿynyh kạn fyhạ ḥb sbạny
 2- ymwt yswʿ rjạyạ ʿạsẖ kẖdt ạlkẖlạṣ mnh bblạsẖ
 wḥạjạt ktyr mạstḥqhạsẖ yswʿ mn ạlmwt njạny
 kl ạlklạm ʿnh mạykfysẖ sẖạl ạlʿqạb wmạḥạsbnysẖ
 ạ̉nạ ạtʿfyt wqạl ly ʿysẖ ḥkm brạʾẗ mjạny</lyrics>
<author>jylạn, jylạn</author>
<hymn_number>11180</hymn_number>
</song>